<view class="container">
  <image src="http://localhost:5001/images/recipe/02.jpg" class="recipe-image" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="recipe-info">
    <text class="recipe-title">孜然羊肉</text>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">所需食材</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ing-list">
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">洋葱块</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">青红椒片</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">花椒面</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">孜然面</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">辣椒面</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">生抽</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">香醋</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">盐适量</text></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">烹饪步骤</text>
      </view>
      <view class="step-list">
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>1</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">取出羊肉，用清水泡化开，沥干水分备用。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>2</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">锅内放油，将羊肉下锅炒干水分，放入洋葱块、青红椒块，加入适量生抽、盐炒熟。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>3</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">加入少许花椒面、适量孜然面和辣椒面，淋少许香醋出锅即可。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>